ails photo essay on aimee semple mcphersons lake elsinore castle retreat the theatricality of revivalism as exemplified in the artistry of billy sunday and aimee semple mcpherson did mcpherson send a minions of satan message to herbert hoover and another article by the same historian later concluding she did not send such a message aimee semple mcpherson on imdb scandal and censure a reinvestigation of the sociopolitical forces surrounding the disappearance of aimee semple mcpherson authority control worldcat identities viaf  lccn n isni     gnd  sudoc  retrieved from httpsenwikipediaorgwindexphptitleaimeesemplemcphersonoldid categories  births deathsthcentury christiansaimee semple mcphersonamerican anticommunistsamerican antifascistsamerican evangelicalsamerican evangelistsamerican pentecostalsamerican people of canadian descentamerican people of irish descentamerican temperance activistsburials at forest lawn memorial park glendalecanadian evangelicalscanadian evangelistscanadian pentecostalscanadian people of irish descentchristian creationistschristian fundamentalistsdrugrelated deaths in californiafaith healershistory of los angelesmembers of the international church of the foursquare gospelpeople from oxford county ontarioreligious scandalsvaudeville performersactivists from californiahidden categories articles that may be too long from october pages using infobox person with unknown parametersinfobox person using religionarticles with hcardswikipedia external links cleanup from november wikipedia spam cleanup from november articles with internet archive linkswikipedia articles with viaf identifierswikipedia articles with lccn identifierswikipedia articles with isni identifierswikipedia articles with gnd identifiers navigation menu personal tools not logged intalkcontributionscreate accountlog in namespaces article talk variants views read edit view history more search navigation main pagecontentsfeatured contentcurrent eventsrandom articledonate to wikipedia