rgerson may   writes in his aimees disappearance remains a mystery story that hc benedict owner of the carmel cottage was expected to be a witness against mcpherson but died apparently of heart trouble before he could testify cox notes that hc benedict did indeed testify but on her behalf denying vehemently the woman with ormiston was mcpherson hc benedict died on november   some weeks after all testimony had been concluded  sutton p   sutton p   timothy tow john sung and the asian awakening articlesochristiancom retrieved    awake and go global prayer network  john sung towelmysitehostedcom retrieved    the real conversion of dr john sung rlhymersjrcom retrieved    george hunston williams rodney lawrence petersen calvin augustine pater the contentious triangle church state and university truman state university press  p   blumhofer pp  lian xi redeemed by fire the rise of popular christianity in modern china yale university press  p   dr edwin louis cole christianmensnetworkcom  retrieved    who is more powerful than the president mobilewndcom  retrieved    sutton pp –  epstein pp  –  sutton p   there is a god debate between aimee semple mcpherson fundamentalist and charles lee smith atheist foursquare publications  glendale blvd los angeles ca   sutton pp –  sutton p   lingeman p   sutton p   a b caleb crain  notebook aimee semple mcpherson steamboats are ruining everything archived from the original on  december  retrieved    aimee canadian musicals retrieved  april    vanity fairs cutout dolls – no  vanity fair archived from the original on  february  retrieved    the voice of hollywood no   on imdb  horwitch lauren february   actor chad allens lead role in a  million backstage backstage llc retrieved january     sister aimee by richard rossi bottletreeinccom retrieved    gilbert brian november   hallelujah how faith healer aimee semple mcpherson inspired the riproaring new musical scandalous broadway buzz broadwaycom retrieved january     gottlieb robert kimbal