thing  epstein pp    a lasting legacy  foursquare legacy  the foursquare church foursquareorg retrieved    sutton pp    cox p  note mcpherson was frequently photographed with the image of the christian cross which differs from the crucifix with its hanging figure of jesus and its common association with catholicism cox states anecdotally some persons adversarial to mcpherson who heard the berle story wanted to believe it was true but that bit about the crucifix convinced them otherwise  sutton p   cox p   cox raymond l the verdict is in  p   blumhofer p   a b roberts liardon gods generals vol  dvd   sutton pp –  a b american experience  sister aimee pbs retrieved    she also traveled to england scotland and wales for five weeks of revival services press reports depending upon the sources described her audiences as either lacking enthusiasm or multitudes filling the altars anxiously awaiting a return visit poor aimee time october   archived from the original on  september  retrieved  those of the nobility and gentry and middle classes who reflected upon the matter appeared to feel that the holy bible still offers a sufficient choice of gospels but of course the london mob the lower classes rushed to attend the evangelistic first night of aimee semple mcpherson   epstein pp –  epstein p   blumhofer pp   note a month later most of the choir members returned their leader gladwyn nichols later returned as well after publicly apologizing to mcpherson  epstein p   epstein p   epstein p   a b epstein p   a b c dr raymond l cox  the greatest nine days oocitiesorg retrieved    epstein p   today in history  october  aimee semple mcpherson uninvited to speak at harvard skepticismorg  retrieved    mcpherson aimee semple give me my own god h c kinsey  company inc   matthew avery sutton aimee semple mcpherson and the resurrection of christian america cambridge harvard university press  p   mcpherson give me my own god pp –  dr raymond l cox  was aimee semple mcpherson pentecostal 