ful preacher aimee semple mcpherson contains her passionate preaching about christ addresses the holy spirit’s indwelling of believers and discusses the importance of jesus’ return mcpherson’s powerful preaching in s los angeles mobilized and attracted a great number of followers this collection illustrates what made her teaching so compelling and will gain a perspective on this influential preacher in american church history these examples from her prodigious output will benefit those who wish to understand her mark on the subsequent charismatic church movement and her season of influential ministry at the angelus temple in the logos editions these volumes are enhanced by amazing functionality important terms link to dictionaries encyclopedias and a wealth of other resources in your digital library perform powerful searches to find exactly what you’re looking for take the discussion with you using tablet and mobile apps with logos bible software the most efficient and comprehensive research tools are in one place so you get the most out of your study for more pentecostalcharismatic resources check out the charisma house bundle key features offers sermons that are both ecumenical and focused on the work of the holy spirit contains evangelical messages that call for decision provides examples of early twentiethcentury charismatic teaching back to top product details title select works of aimee semple mcpherson author aimee semple mcpherson volumes  pages  christian group pentecostalcharismatic resource type collected works topic practical life back to top individual titles the second coming of christ is he coming how is he coming when is he coming for whom is he coming divine healing sermons this is that personal experiences sermons and writings of aimee semple mcpherson evangelist back to top the second coming of christ is he coming how is he coming when is he coming for whom is he coming author aimee semple mcpherson publisher aimee semple mcpherson publication date  pages  sample pages              this scripturally supported study of the return of jesus provides readers with clear evidence for jesus’ imminent return because much of mcpherson’s preaching up to  sermons a week was focused on moving her audience to a decision her writing is also filled with many moving examples and illustrations that teach to the heart modern christians will see timeless truths in a new way and will better understand the weighty implications of jesus’ promise to return as reigning king divine healing sermons author aimee semple mcpherson publisher aimee semple mcpherson publication date  pages  sample pages              this volume contains hopefilled sermons on the themes of god’s work in the modern world the scriptural relationship between salvation and healing frequently asked questions about divine healing and more these sermons are filled with powerful rhetoric and turns of phrase that assist readers and hearers to live in light of god’s word this is that personal experiences sermons and writings of aimee semple mcpherson evangelist author aimee semple mcpherson publisher bridal call publishing house publication date  pages  sample pages              this book contains the story of aimee semple mcpherson from simple agrarian life to nationwide fame as a preacher and teacher this account includes her baptism in the holy spirit evangelistic campaigns and ministry career readers will benefit from her story as well as her teaching in this focused study back to top about aimee semple mcpherson aimee semple mcpherson – was a prominent evangelist in los angeles and founder of the international church of the foursquare gospel she performed public healings promoted the idea of america as a nation particularly blessed by god engaged in charity work and became a model that many charismatic churches emulated and followed her ministry casts a long shadow on this movement within the modern american church back to top more details about these resources 